---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy — IMTI" description="Privacy Policy for India Market Timing Index">
  <div class="card" style="max-width:800px;">
    <h1 style="font-size:24px;margin-bottom:16px;">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p style="color:var(--text-secondary);font-size:13px;margin-bottom:24px;">Last updated: April 23, 2026</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:18px;margin:24px 0 12px;">1. Introduction</h2>
    <p>India Market Timing Index ("IMTI", "we", "us") respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our website.</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:18px;margin:24px 0 12px;">2. Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul style="margin-left:20px;color:var(--text-secondary);">
      <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> When you sign in with Google, we receive your email, name, and profile photo from Firebase Authentication.</li>
      <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> We collect anonymized page views and interaction data via Google Analytics (with your consent).</li>
      <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> We use essential cookies for site functionality and optional cookies for analytics/ads with your consent.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 style="font-size:18px;margin:24px 0 12px;">3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
    <ul style="margin-left:20px;color:var(--text-secondary);">
      <li>To provide personalized features (watchlists, saved preferences) via Firestore</li>
      <li>To improve our website and content</li>
      <li>To display relevant advertisements (only with explicit consent)</li>
      <li>To send email updates if you subscribe</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 style="font-size:18px;margin:24px 0 12px;">4. Data Storage</h2>
    <p>Your data is stored securely in <strong>Google Firebase</strong> (Firestore and Authentication). Firebase complies with GDPR and SOC 2 standards. We do not sell your personal data to third parties.</p>

    <h2 style="font-size:18px;margin:24px 0 12px;">5. Your Rights (DPDP Act 2023)</h2>
    <p>Under India's Digital Personal Data Protection Act 2023, you have the right to:</p>
    <ul style="margin-left:20px;color:var(--text-secondary);">
      <li>Access your personal data</li>
      <li>Request correction or deletion</li>
      <li>Withdraw consent for non-essential processing</li>
      <li>File a complaint with the Data Protection Board of India</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 style="font-size:18px;margin:24px 0 12px;">6. Contact</h2>
    <p>For privacy-related queries, email <a href="mailto:support@imti.in">support@imti.in</a>.</p>
  </div>
</Layout>
